The paper discusses the particularities of software testing in game development, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) category. The study also involves analyzing game balance, game physics, and entertainment-related aspects, which could be related to graphics (cs.GR), human-computer interaction (cs.HC), cybersecurity (cs.CY), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
